Privacy Policy
We, Ador.com (thereinafter “Ador”) know you care how information about you is used and shared. We respect your privacy and take your online safety seriously.
ADOR
In order to provide you with the products and services, we collect and process your essential personal data at minimum scale from the Ador website, services, online stores, and applications. When you use any of our Services (as defined below) you are consenting to the practices described in the Privacy Policy. Mostly, we will communicate with you electronically in a variety of ways, such as by e-mail, text, in-app push notices or by posting e-mail messages or communications on the website or through the other services and electronic communication.
ADOR
For contractual purposes, you agree that all agreements, notices, disclosures and other communications that we provide you electronically satisfy any legal requirement that such communications be in writing, unless mandatory applicable laws specifically require a different form of communication.
ADOR
Thank you for accessing the website, mobile applicationsand other software of Ador (collectively, the "Service"). We respect your privacy and want you to know about the Privacy Policy taken to protect your personal information. If you have any questions regarding collecting or processing of your personal data, please contact us by e-mail at dataprotectionofficer@ador.com.
