) or Customer Service.
* Withdrawal of consent.
You may withdraw you consent to the processing of your data at any time, but you shall be realized that the withdrawal of the consent will not affect the lawfulness of processing regarding consent before the withdrawal.
Whenever we transfer personal information to countries beyond European Union in the course of sharing information, we will transfer that information in accordance with this Privacy Policy and as permitted by the applicable laws on data protection.
